Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}啊！这样根本不会有进展\N{\fnArial\fs48}Guh! This isn't getting us anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.66,0:00:07.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}怎么了，“煎饺”？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What's the matter, perogie?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.36,0:00:07.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你累了？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.96,0:00:10.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不要疲惫，我只要结果\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't get tired. I get results.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“拉我起来”的标志是晃一下还是晃两下？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Was the sign for "pull me up" one wiggle or two?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:19.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，保持注意力\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, stay focused.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.01,0:00:22.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就我们所知，青金石和碧玉的融合体\N{\fnArial\fs48}For all we know, Lapis and Jasper's fusion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.18,0:00:23.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}可能就在眼前\N{\fnArial\fs48}could be right under our noses.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:28.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这就是我们要穿救生衣的原因\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is why we wear life jackets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.08,0:00:30.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Are -- are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.52,0:00:32.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么也没有\N{\fnArial\fs48}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，感觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, it feels like
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.86,0:00:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们已经搜索了好几“光年”了\N{\fnArial\fs48}we've been searching for light years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.09,0:00:40.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，“光年”测的是光\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, light years measures light.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.09,0:00:41.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是年\N{\fnArial\fs48} Not years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.13,0:00:46.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我受够这些...“就剩尿布”了\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I'm sick of these...Life diapers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:49.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}安全不是玩笑，珍珠\N{\fnArial\fs48}Safety is no punch line, Pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:51.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}安全就是我们的任务\N{\fnArial\fs48}Safety {\i1}is{\i} our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.18,0:00:52.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们必须找到青金石和碧玉\N{\fnArial\fs48}We must find Jasper and Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.84,0:00:53.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}只要还存在\N{\fnArial\fs48}As it stands,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们的融合体就是定时炸弹\N{\fnArial\fs48}their fusion is a ticking time bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:58.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石不会出事吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is Lapis gonna be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她使用能力将她们的融合体\N{\fnArial\fs48}She had control when she used her power
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.46,0:01:02.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}拖入海中时，她是清醒的\N{\fnArial\fs48}to drag their fusion into the ocean,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是，像她们那样由猜忌和愤怒\N{\fnArial\fs48}but a fusion like theirs is unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:07.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}束缚在一起融合体是不稳定的\N{\fnArial\fs48}bound together by anger and mistrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.66,0:01:08.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一旦约束被打破\N{\fnArial\fs48}If that bond snaps,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她们的愤怒会彻底释放，摧毁一切\N{\fnArial\fs48}their anger will take over and destroy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:14.23,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要担心，青金石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't worry, Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们不会让你和鱼群入睡的\N{\fnArial\fs48}We won't let you sleep with the fishes.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.23,0:01:16.46,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}短语“sleep with fish”出自著名黑手党电影“The Godfather”（教父）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.47,0:01:20.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们得继续搜索\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're gonna have to keep looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但首先，我们要把史蒂文带回家\N{\fnArial\fs48}But first, let's bring Steven home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:24.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh? What? Wha?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不。我-我-我没事\N{\fnArial\fs48}No. I'm -- I'm -- I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.81,0:01:28.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一起-一起钓鱼吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let's -- let's go fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.34,0:01:31.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}第一个抓到东西的获胜\N{\fnArial\fs48}First one to catch something wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我赢了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I win.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:31.55,0:01:32.62,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}此处Steven的姿势致敬”Final Fantasy“（最终幻想系列）中的Cactuar（仙人掌）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.34,0:01:35.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们本应在外面搜索\N{\fnArial\fs48}We should be out there searching,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:37.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而不是在这里发呆\N{\fnArial\fs48}not in here not searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:42.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}睡眠是诅咒，一个必须承受的诅咒\N{\fnArial\fs48}Sleep is a curse, and yet a curse I need to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.02,0:01:43.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}——史蒂文·宇宙\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:45.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文不像我们\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven isn't like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.03,0:01:46.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他需要休息\N{\fnArial\fs48}He needs rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:48.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们就不用休息吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't you guys need rest, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们看起来很疲惫\N{\fnArial\fs48}You look exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:52.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们好极了\N{\fnArial\fs48}We look awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}听着，没试过\N{\fnArial\fs48}Look, you can't really knock sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.17,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就没有发言权\N{\fnArial\fs48}until you try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:01:59.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且，也许我们可以搞个有趣的\N{\fnArial\fs48}And maybe we can throw a little fun into the mix
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:01.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}睡衣派对！\N{\fnArial\fs48}with a slumber party!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:02.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}有-有趣？\N{\fnArial\fs48}F-fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:03.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}对啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:05.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们所有人一起，安详的眯一觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}All of us together, peacefully dozing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就当外面没有\N{\fnArial\fs48}It'll be like there isn't
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.50,0:02:10.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个满是复仇念头的融合体在用仇恨煮沸大海\N{\fnArial\fs48}a vengeful fusion boiling the ocean with hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文是对的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:14.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们应该呆在家休息，但我得离开\N{\fnArial\fs48}You should stay here and relax, but I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:16.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}因为我永远都是放松的\N{\fnArial\fs48}'Cause I'm always relaxed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.36,0:02:19.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但石榴，你不可能\N{\fnArial\fs48}But Garnet, you couldn't possibly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.04,0:02:20.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}一个人搜索整片海洋\N{\fnArial\fs48}search the ocean by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.36,0:02:24.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我-让我们帮你吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me -- let {\i1}us{\i} help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:25.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们是一个团队\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:26.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不用\N{\fnArial\fs48}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:29.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在你们是一个团队-睡衣团队\N{\fnArial\fs48}Right now, you're a party -- a slumber party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.68,0:02:31.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，带着些宝石人上床\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, put these gems to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.82,0:02:33.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要熬夜哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't stay up too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}冰箱里有零食\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's snacks in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:36.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}再见\N{\fnArial\fs48}Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.78,0:02:39.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在，在开始睡衣派对之前\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now, before we get this slumber party started,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.21,0:02:41.91,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你们有人想要睡衣伙伴吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}would either of you care for a slumber companion?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.10,0:02:42.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不用\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:47.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48} Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不需要睡衣伙伴\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll pass on the slumber pals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.39,0:02:51.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧。入睡吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay. Sleep it up, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.49,0:02:52.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，好吧\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:55.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这样对吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Is this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不，你得躺下\N{\fnArial\fs48}No, you should lay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.80,0:03:01.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这样对吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Am I doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，这比刚才好多了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, that's way better than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.38,0:03:05.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但，一定要保持闭眼\N{\fnArial\fs48}But close your eyes all the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.60,0:03:10.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好。好的。我在睡觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay. All right. I'm sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我在睡觉\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.66,0:03:13.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你睡觉时不能说话\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't talk while you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}到底怎么才能入睡？\N{\fnArial\fs48}How's this even supposed to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.75,0:03:16.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这很简单\N{\fnArial\fs48}It's easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:21.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你只要躺下，怎么舒服怎么来，不要乱动\N{\fnArial\fs48}You just lie down, get nice and comfy, don't move,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:26.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且不要想任何事情\N{\fnArial\fs48}and don't think about anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“宇宙小子”在演播室现场观众面前实时录制\N{\fnArial\fs48}{\i1}Steven Universe was filmed{\i} {\i1}before a live studio audience.{\i}
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.29,0:03:29.63,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}格雷格说的话在美式情景喜剧片头经常使用。\N石榴在梦中的表现类似“Happy Days”（欢乐时光）中的Arthur Fonzarelli（“The Fonz”）——经典的"Aaay！"入场词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.63,0:03:30.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我的天哪，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my goodness,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.70,0:03:32.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}康妮马上就到了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Connie's going to be here any second now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.93,0:03:33.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我简直不敢相信\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你的第一次校园舞会!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Your first school dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让我调整一下你的领带并-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Let me just fix your tie and --
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:39.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别再把史蒂文当个宝宝拉\N{\fnArial\fs48}Stop fussing over Steven like a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.34,0:03:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，我是怎么跟你说的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, what did I tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.00,0:03:42.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别在屋里滑那个\N{\fnArial\fs48}about riding that thing in the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}祝你舞会玩的愉快，伙计\N{\fnArial\fs48}Have fun at your dance, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh! Bungacowa!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.35,0:03:46.94,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}“Bungacowa！”是“Cowabunga！”的倒装词。这是美漫中一个表达兴奋的惯用语。\N最初起源于漫画“Peanuts”（或叫史努比），并由”TMNT“（忍者神龟）和Bart Simpson（巴特-辛普森一家）发扬光大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:49.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶，别让我抓到你！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst, I'm gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.60,0:03:50.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}马上，康妮\N{\fnArial\fs48}Just a second, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.10,0:03:54.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你绝对猜不到紫晶刚刚-蛤？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You won't believe what Amethyst just -- huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.99,0:03:56.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我能为你做什么吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}该放松了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Chille tid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.96,0:04:03.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，你好，石榴——嘿，史蒂文\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, hi, Garnet. Hey, Steven.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你今晚一定要来沙滩上\N{\fnArial\fs48}You got to come to the beach tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.83,0:04:07.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}到时会有个篝火派对哦！\N{\fnArial\fs48}There's gonna be this huge bonfire party thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.30,0:04:08.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我去不了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't go to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:11.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我要和康妮参加一个大型舞会呢\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm going to the big dance with Connie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.40,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，盛大的舞会\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wow. The big dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:15.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}别做出格的事哦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't do anything I wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.28,0:04:19.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她来了！\N{\fnArial\fs48} She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:22.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好啦，我准备好去跳舞了，康-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Okay, I'm ready for the big dance con--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:22.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃？\N{\fnArial\fs48}huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:25.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.06,0:04:32.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48} Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:33.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ah! Ugh! 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.62,0:04:35.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，妈呀...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:38.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我睡着了，然后做了个奇怪的梦\N{\fnArial\fs48}I feel asleep and had this weird dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.54,0:04:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我打开门，青金石在门外，然后-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I opened the door and Lapis was there, and --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，这听起来毫无逻辑\N{\fnArial\fs48}well, that doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:45.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石正和碧玉在海底融合在一起\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis is fused with Jasper at the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:48.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你从没做过梦吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}You've never had a dream before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:50.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦...我觉得没有\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.90,0:04:53.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，珍珠，梦并不总是合理的\N{\fnArial\fs48}Well, Pearl, dreams don't always make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.40,0:04:56.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}当你作梦时，你脑中的想法\N{\fnArial\fs48}When you dream, the thoughts in your head
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.24,0:04:58.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}混合在一起，组成一部诡异的影片\N{\fnArial\fs48}get all mixed up into a weird movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并且它们很难解释，\N{\fnArial\fs48}And they're really hard to explain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.96,0:05:01.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}让其看起来很无聊\N{\fnArial\fs48}which is why they're boring to listen to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就像，有一次，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Like.this one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我做了个梦，好像，有些东西\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had a dream where, like, these things
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}挂在甜甜圈店里出售，对吧？\N{\fnArial\fs48}were being sold at the big donut, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但是甜甜圈店的前门\N{\fnArial\fs48}But the front door of the big donut shop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:13.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}却连接到了我爸面包车的后面\N{\fnArial\fs48}led to the back of my dad's van.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:15.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}于是，我走进了面包车，\N{\fnArial\fs48}So, I go into the van,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:19.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后狮子因为某些原因在开车，但...\N{\fnArial\fs48}and Lion is driving for some reason, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}...他开得非常好\N{\fnArial\fs48}...he's driving really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:25.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}然后-然后我对他说，我说，“狮子-”\N{\fnArial\fs48}And -- and then I say to him, I says, "Lion --"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:31.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“狮子，你是怎么学会开面-面包车的？”\N{\fnArial\fs48}"Lion, how did you learn to drive you a v-van?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:32.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}”你甚至不能“\N{\fnArial\fs48}You can't even...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:37.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}“你...你都不能给我...我的...”\N{\fnArial\fs48}You...You can't bring...Me...My...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.74,0:05:41.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoo!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:39.74,0:05:42.74,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,200)}此处史蒂文用背上的螺旋桨飞行的画面致敬“Karlsson on the Roof”（屋顶上的小飞人）中的“Karlsson”（卡尔松）。“Karlsson on the Roof”是一部由瑞典作家Astrid Lindgren创作的儿童系列读物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.50,0:05:44.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狗升机！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Dogcopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:47.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}先生，我是您最忠实的粉丝之一！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mr. copter, sir, I'm one of your biggest fans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.68,0:05:49.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}求求你能给我个签名吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can I please have your autograph?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:53.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}狗升机先生，求求您-嘿，等等我！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Mr. copter, please -- hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}您要去哪？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:58.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我希望小报中有关狗升机先生的流言\N{\fnArial\fs48}I hope the rumors about dogcopter in the tabloids
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}都不是真的\N{\fnArial\fs48}aren't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:01.94,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗯？哦，嘿，珍珠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Huh? Oh, hey, Pearl!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.40,0:06:04.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等...别吃我啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait...Don't eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噗！唔！哦，天哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ptoo! Ooh! Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}谢谢你给的升级组件，珍珠！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Thanks for the upgrade, Pearl!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.50,0:06:09.34,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,70)}这个很明显了，”Astro Boy“（铁臂阿童木）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在我能追上狗-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now I can catch up with dog--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}喔，紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}whoa. Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:18.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这一切，真的开始变得诡异了\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is getting really weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:19.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这确实很诡异\N{\fnArial\fs48}This {\i1}is{\i} weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，那声音听起来很像-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, that sounds a lot like --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.04,0:06:23.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.14,0:06:24.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis Lazuli!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，你-你在这干什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, wh-what are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:30.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃，我知道这听起来很怪，但我正在做梦，\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh, I know it's weird, but I'm just dreaming,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:32.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以不用担心\N{\fnArial\fs48}so don't even worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.11,0:06:33.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}什么？不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}What? No!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:36.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，我正试着集中注意力\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, I'm trying to concentrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.18,0:06:37.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你怎么会在这里？\N{\fnArial\fs48} How are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.78,0:06:39.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦，我的天哪，你还好吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, my gosh. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，求求你，我-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, please, I --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...青金石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh...  Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:48.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.16,0:06:51.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘿，你在笑什么？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hey, what are you laughing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢，罗丝！这真是太好了！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh, Rose! This is wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:07:01.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}跟你在一起非常开心，罗丝！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm just having so much fun spending time with you, Rose!
Dialogue: 1,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.00,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}这个太明显了，”Titanic“（泰坦尼克号）中Jack和Rose（啧啧）在船首的镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}忘了格雷格吧，我们一起在银河系旅游！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Forget about Greg. Let's go travel the galaxy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:07.88,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠，非常感谢你...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl, thank you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}修好我的车！\N{\fnArial\fs48}For fixing my van!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.88,0:07:10.05,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}详见第一季第27集
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.05,0:07:11.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦！啊！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呕...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Blegh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:14.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}恶...\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}珍珠？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:21.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...好的，史蒂文？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh... Yes, Steven?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我又做了，一个有关青金石的梦\N{\fnArial\fs48}I had another dream about Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:27.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢...没什么！梦不是真实的！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh...That's okay! Dreams aren't real!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那只是拼接电影！\N{\fnArial\fs48}They're just mixed-up movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:32.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但我-我觉得我当时在和她对话\N{\fnArial\fs48}But I -- I think I was talking to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.24,0:07:34.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，你怎么知道的？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:37.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不知道，但我能感觉到\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't, but I could just feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:38.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她在喊叫\N{\fnArial\fs48}She was yelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:40.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并且她真的受到刺激了\N{\fnArial\fs48}and she was really freaked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.01,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}她说了什么？她还能控制住吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}What did she say? Is she still in control?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我...我不知道\N{\fnArial\fs48}I...I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:48.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，你刚才可能通过你的梦境\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you could be using your dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.22,0:07:50.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}与她进行了心灵感应\N{\fnArial\fs48}to connect with her mentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你能再做一次吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can you do it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.73,0:07:54.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许青金石刚好能告诉你她们在哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Maybe Lapis can just tell you where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:56.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我猜我又得入睡了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I guess I have to go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快，珍珠，告诉我你的梦\N{\fnArial\fs48}Quick, Pearl, tell me about your dream
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.03,0:08:00.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}帮我入睡\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I can fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我的梦？\N{\fnArial\fs48}M-my dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:04.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}来啊，珍珠！这是为了大局！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Come on, Pearl! It's for the greater good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.76,0:08:06.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我必须的话\N{\fnArial\fs48}If I must.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:10.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}好吧，在我的梦里，我正-\N{\fnArial\fs48} So, in my dream, I was --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:10.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}哦？\N{\fnArial\fs48} What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:12.92,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48} Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.16,0:08:14.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}他这就睡着了\N{\fnArial\fs48}He {\i1}been{\i} sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.00,0:08:19.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢！我知道这已经是梦了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oh! I know this is a dream now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:22.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}那么我能想象出任何我想要的\N{\fnArial\fs48}so I can imagine anything I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:25.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃...土豆泥\N{\fnArial\fs48}Uh...Mashed potato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:26.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:28.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}现在，我该怎么找到青金石？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Now how do I find Lapis?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:29.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是青金石\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:31.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是青金石～\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:32.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不是青金石-\N{\fnArial\fs48}Not Lapis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}呃！狮子？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ugh! Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:37.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，你不是狮子\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait. You're not Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:39.57,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嗷，这是什么地方？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ow. What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.70,0:08:44.44,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石！\N{\fnArial\fs48} Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.90,0:08:45.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你为什么总是-跑回来?!\N{\fnArial\fs48}Why do you keep coming back?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.78,0:08:47.96,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,140)}此处青金石与碧玉被链条连接在一起的设定致敬”Jojo's Bizarre Adventure“（Jojo奇幻大冒险）中的Chain Necklace Deathmatch（项链死斗）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不能被分心！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't get distracted!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.32,0:08:51.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-我得把我们困在海底\N{\fnArial\fs48}I-I've got to hold us down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:53.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}借助你的星球的-海洋-的重量\N{\fnArial\fs48}with the weight of your planet's ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我-必须-将她...\N{\fnArial\fs48} I've got to keep her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:58.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}等等，青金石，告诉我你们在哪\N{\fnArial\fs48}Wait, Lapis, tell me where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.66,0:08:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们能帮你\N{\fnArial\fs48}We can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:03.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我告诉过你！不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}I told you! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:04.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:13.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是你！！！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}碧玉！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Jasper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:16.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是你！！！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:18.78,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你-你！\N{\fnArial\fs48}You! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:20.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Gaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:23.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}噢！不！！！！！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Ohh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:27.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.58,0:09:28.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你看不出来吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:31.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不能停下来，哪怕一秒也不行\N{\fnArial\fs48}I can't stop, not for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.56,0:09:32.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}不要再找我了\N{\fnArial\fs48}Don't look for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.14,0:09:35.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不想要你的帮助。但-\N{\fnArial\fs48}I don't want your help. B-but --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}就让我为你做这些吧！\N{\fnArial\fs48}just let me do this for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.42,0:09:39.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石...不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis... No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:41.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我不再是...青金石了\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'm not Lapis anymore.
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.63,0:09:43.54,Label Trans,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,80)}有没有感觉此处像是“Naruto”（火影忍者）漫画与动画中的Zetsu（绝）吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我们现在是，孔雀石\N{\fnArial\fs48}We're Malachite now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石，不！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:55.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}\N{\fnArial\fs48}Oooragh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.34,0:10:01.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}快走！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.14,0:10:02.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}青金石！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Lapis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.06,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，没事了，我们就在这\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, it's okay. We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.32,0:10:06.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你看到她了吗？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Did you see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}是的，她还在融合体中\N{\fnArial\fs48}Yeah. She's still fused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且她还能控制住，但我不知道还能坚持多久\N{\fnArial\fs48}And she's still in control, but I don't know for how long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:12.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}并且-\N{\fnArial\fs48}And --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这，真是个奇怪的派对\N{\fnArial\fs48}This is a weird party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴！\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet! Mm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:20.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}史蒂文，你还没睡着\N{\fnArial\fs48}Steven, you're still awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:22.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}紫晶刚才在滑滑板\N{\fnArial\fs48}Amethyst was on a skateboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:24.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}接着狗升机对着我“喵”了一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}And then dogcopter meowed at me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.16,0:10:26.52,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}而且对我说的没有任何兴趣！\N{\fnArial\fs48}and was just not interested in what I had to say at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:28.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}也许我有些问题需要解决...\N{\fnArial\fs48}And I might have some issues I need to work out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但青金石，她就在外面，而且他仍然-\N{\fnArial\fs48}But Lapis, she's out there, and she's still --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}嘘～嘘～嘘～嘘——\N{\fnArial\fs48}shh, shh, shh, shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.66,0:10:33.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我知道你很担心，\N{\fnArial\fs48}I know you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}但现在我们什么也做不了\N{\fnArial\fs48}but there's nothing we can do right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}所以让我们放松一下\N{\fnArial\fs48}So let's take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:40.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我来告诉你们该怎么做\N{\fnArial\fs48}I'll show you how it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}这还真有说服力啊\N{\fnArial\fs48}That's pretty convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}石榴？\N{\fnArial\fs48}Garnet?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}如果我可以做到\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ If I could begin to be
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}你对我期望的一半\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ half of what you think of me
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:57.11,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我愿意做任何事\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I could do about anything
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.21,0:11:02.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\fn微软雅黑\fs64}我愿学会像你一样，去爱\N{\fnArial\fs48}♪ I could even learn how to love like you ♪
